This is a Unity 6 mobile game called Toy War Rush.
- Language: C#
- Architecture: Singleton managers, ScriptableObjects, Event-driven
- Pattern: ObjectPool for all spawned objects
- Always use [SerializeField] for inspector fields, never public
- Always null-check before using Instance references
- Use TMP (TextMeshPro) for all UI text
- All coroutines must have cancellation handling
- Mobile: avoid Update() allocations, cache component references in Awake()
